rfkiller is a gnome-shell extension to manage the rfkill devices.

=== Requirements ===
gnome-shell
urfkill

=== Installation ===
Install RFKiller@glin.suse.com to the system extension dir

/usr/share/gnome-shell/extensions

or the local dir

 ~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions

=== How To Use ===
Just press the hotkey (WLAN/BLUETOOTH/WWAN) on the laptop keyboard
